    <item>
      <title>特朗普升级了全球贸易战，引发了卖山雀的关税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-04/trump-s-canada-mexico-china-tariffs-hit-in-deepening-trade-war</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统施加了他对加拿大和墨西哥的威胁，并以全面的进口征税征收，并对中国的现有指控增加了一倍，这激发了迅速报复，这使世界经济陷入了深入的贸易战争。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-04/trump-s-canada-mexico-china-tariffs-hit-in-deepening-trade-war</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Mar 2025 05:01:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>全球资金逃离时，印度股票历史性失败了</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-04/indian-stocks-face-historic-losing-streak-as-foreigners-flee</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度股票的抛售标志着另一个严峻的里程碑，在海外投资者不断销售的情况下，基准指数连续第10天下降。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-04/indian-stocks-face-historic-losing-streak-as-foreigners-flee</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Mar 2025 04:20:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着贸易战的恶化增强对避风港资产的需求，黄金上升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-04/gold-holds-gain-as-trump-stokes-haven-buying-with-tariff-moves</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统施加威胁要袭击加拿大和墨西哥之后，黄金玫瑰（Gold Rose），并以巨大的关税袭击了中国，并迅速报复了中国。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-04/gold-holds-gain-as-trump-stokes-haven-buying-with-tariff-moves</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Mar 2025 00:26:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>弗雷斯尼乌斯（Fresenius）筹集了11亿欧元的透析公司</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-03/fresenius-seeks-1-1-billion-for-stake-in-dialysis-company</link>
      <description><![CDATA[弗雷森乌斯·塞（Fresenius SE）在出售弗雷斯尼乌斯医疗服务公司（Fresenius Medical Care AG）的股票以及与透析公司相关的可交换债券中筹集了近11亿欧元（12亿美元），因为它希望削减债务和重新分配资本。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-03/fresenius-seeks-1-1-billion-for-stake-in-dialysis-company</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Mar 2025 17:53:56 GMT</pubDate>
